<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
		<div style="font-size:20px;font-style:italic;font-weight:bold">Please do not reply to this email!</div>
    <h4>Reminder for the upcoming event: <%= @event.name %></h4>
    <p>This is a friendly reminder that the date for the event is <%= @event.display_start_time %>. </p>
		<p>You may update your rsvp response (e.g. Number of additional guest you are bringing, your rsvp comment and/or what you are bringing to the party) and/or view the event details (like location, start time) by clicking <%= link_to 'here', event_url(@event, :auth_token => @attendee.authentication_token) %>.</p>
		<p>  If you have an account, please login to <%= link_to 'Lets Gather', root_url %> and do so ASAP to inform the host of any changes from your end.   You may also contact your host at <%= @event.user.email %> for any further inquiries.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>

